Thing's only got a few good games(but all with bad audio issues, holy jebus) and a buncha shovelware to pad the title roster to boast that impressive sounding 50+ game list. Just buy a refurbished Genesis, probably find a cartridge for it that you can load ROM files onto(or buy the games too if they don't break your bank), and bam. Infinitely better value and use than the crummy 50 dollar knockoff Genesis. Lol.

My whole point here? Bobby should got a point for that smash.
